<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to ToCry!</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@picocss/pico@2/css/pico.min.css" />
    <style>
        body { display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; min-height: 100vh; margin: 0; background-color: var(--pico-background-color); }
        article { text-align: center; padding: 2rem; border-radius: var(--pico-border-radius); background-color: var(--pico-card-background-color); box-shadow: var(--pico-card-box-shadow); }
        h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        p { font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
        .button-group {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <article>
        <h1>Welcome to ToCry!</h1>
        <p>ToCry is a simple, self-hosted Kanban-style TODO application designed to help you manage your tasks efficiently.</p>
        <p>To access your boards and start organizing your tasks, please log in.</p>
        <div class="button-group">
            <a href="/auth/google" role="button">Login with Google</a>
            <a href="https://tocry.ralsina.me" role="button" class="secondary outline">Learn more about ToCry</a>
        </div>
    </article>
</body>
</html>
